{"title":"朝鲜谚语","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":3,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝鲜谚语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泰山之高扬名天下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却屹立在苍空下面；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们并不去攀登它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只仰望着山顶埋怨泰山高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有趟过河水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能知道水的深浅；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有长期相处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能了解人的心底。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"＊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果唠唠叨叨话多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有用的话便少；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果只是忙忙碌碌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做出的好事并不多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李炯远辑译"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}